  "text": "The long-term outcome for most children with progressive/metastatic rhabdomyosarcoma (RMS) has remained dismal for more than 4 decades [CITATION_1] . While temsirolimus offers a short-term survival benefit [CITATION_2] , new approaches for improved long term survival benefit are needed.",
